videos.headline: South Carolina's Bryant flies in for putback poster

videos.description: Immanuel Quickley has a wide-open look to tie the game late, but can't get the shot to go, which is followed by several missed Kentucky layups.
videos.headline: Quickley misses game-tying 3-point attempt

videos.description: Kentucky ties the score at one end, but South Carolina's Jermaine Couisnard banks in a 3-pointer at the horn to lift the Gamecocks.
